# PyInstaller
#  Usually these files are created by a PyInstaller script from a 'spec' file
#  often created by 'pyi-makespec'
#  Still, sometimes a user chooses to use PyInstaller from the command line
#  and run PyInstaller from the root of the source tree, generating some of these
#  files either in 'dist' or in the root of the tree.
*.spec

